Melee (Dharok's)=
[[Dharok the Wretched's equipment]] with [[absorption]]s requires more attention than the other setups, but offers the fastest [[Attack]] and [[Strength]] [[experience]] of up to 180,000 experience per hour using [[dragon claws]] for [[special attack]]s during Power Surge, or up to 155,000 with a [[Granite maul#Ornate handle|granite maul with an ornate handle]]. It is recommended to only use the setup with {{SCP|Hitpoints|92|link=yes}} or greater because of the set effect increasing damage when missing more HP. Switches can be brought for strength bonus during Power Surge. The rest of the equipment maximises strength and accuracy bonuses. It is possible to sustain around 1 hour per dream with this setup.

